        "| Batch | Input Tokens | Output Tokens | Total | Cost |",
        "|-------|-------------|--------------|-------|------|",
        f"| J26-640 | {j640.get('input_tokens',0):,} | {j640.get('output_tokens',0):,} | {j640.get('input_tokens',0)+j640.get('output_tokens',0):,} | ${j640.get('cost_usd','?')} |",
        f"| J26-788 | {j788.get('input_tokens',0):,} | {j788.get('output_tokens',0):,} | {j788.get('input_tokens',0)+j788.get('output_tokens',0):,} | ${j788.get('cost_usd','?')} |",
